/**
 * ðŸ’° USDTg Native Coin - Pure USDTgVerse Implementation
 * ===================================================
 * 
 * âš›ï¸ QUANTUM-SAFE NATIVE TOKEN
 * ðŸš€ OPTIMIZED FOR USDTGVM
 * ðŸŒ CROSS-CHAIN BRIDGE COMPATIBLE
 * 
 * This is the NATIVE implementation using USDTgScript language,
 * completely independent from Ethereum/Solidity ecosystem.
